WEBVTT

01:55.840 --> 01:56.950
Your Highness,

01:57.350 --> 01:58.400
last night,

01:58.870 --> 02:00.310
you and Liu Chu...

02:06.230 --> 02:07.680
From this moment on,

02:08.080 --> 02:10.190
you are his true concubine.

02:11.630 --> 02:13.280
Rank doesn't matter.

02:13.800 --> 02:14.840
What matters

02:14.840 --> 02:16.630
is that he keeps loving me.

02:18.360 --> 02:19.680
I’m sure he will.

02:21.870 --> 02:22.680
By the way, Your Highness,

02:22.680 --> 02:23.150
Yes?

02:23.870 --> 02:26.430
I'm leaving the palace today.

02:30.000 --> 02:30.960
So soon?

02:31.680 --> 02:32.470
Yes.

02:32.840 --> 02:35.630
Lan said she has found
a place for me to stay.【】

02:36.560 --> 02:38.820
She hopes I can leave as soon as possible.

02:40.240 --> 02:40.840
Well...

02:41.000 --> 02:42.030
Don't worry.

02:42.240 --> 02:45.300
Now that you and Liu Chu
have shared your wedding night,

02:45.430 --> 02:46.760
I can finally be at ease.

02:48.470 --> 02:50.030
What if I miss you?

02:50.870 --> 02:51.870
I told you.

02:52.150 --> 02:54.480
I’ll come back to visit you
as soon as I can.

02:55.870 --> 02:56.960
Really?

02:57.840 --> 02:58.470
Yes.

03:04.630 --> 03:05.960
Such a beauty—

03:05.960 --> 03:07.690
who could help but fall in love?

03:10.800 --> 03:11.860
Then in the future,

03:12.190 --> 03:14.190
I’ll have to find you the perfect husband,

03:14.190 --> 03:16.079
and marry you off in grand style.

03:19.630 --> 03:21.150
I still prefer

03:22.560 --> 03:23.870
Changmo men.

03:26.079 --> 03:26.470
Then...

03:26.470 --> 03:28.280
Lord Fei has no chance, right?

03:36.190 --> 03:37.280
Because Miss Jin Xi

03:37.280 --> 03:39.000
is Consort Ling's female official.

03:39.000 --> 03:41.030
the Grand Princess specially ordered
the palace gates opened wide

03:41.030 --> 03:42.079
and personally saw her off

03:42.079 --> 03:43.610
with the highest courtesy.

03:43.750 --> 03:45.870
Not everyone gets this kind of treatment.

03:45.870 --> 03:47.560
Then please, Miss Lan,

03:47.560 --> 03:49.280
convey my thanks
to the Grand Princess for me.

03:49.280 --> 03:50.470
I certainly will.

03:51.800 --> 03:53.150
When I'm not around,

03:53.470 --> 03:55.840
if anyone dares to bully the Princess,

03:56.000 --> 03:58.460
I definitely won't
let them get away with it.

03:58.470 --> 04:01.080
Consort Ling is the person
the Emperor cares about the most.

04:01.080 --> 04:01.960
In this palace,

04:01.960 --> 04:03.870
who would dare to bully her?

04:04.630 --> 04:05.190
Okay.

04:05.750 --> 04:07.150
Then I am relieved.

04:09.870 --> 04:11.000
Jin Xi,

04:12.080 --> 04:13.610
take good care of yourself.

04:15.080 --> 04:15.870
Take care.

04:20.630 --> 04:22.240
Bring Miss Jin Xi’s luggage.

04:28.160 --> 04:28.950
Jin Xi,

04:30.920 --> 04:32.450
you must come back to see me.

04:54.480 --> 04:55.610
Where are you going?

04:55.800 --> 04:56.870
I'm going to see Mo.

04:57.159 --> 04:57.890
Don't worry.

04:58.190 --> 05:00.070
Liu Xiyang will take good care of him.

05:00.070 --> 05:01.310
Do you need something from me?

05:01.310 --> 05:01.910
Follow me.

05:30.190 --> 05:31.950
Where is this place?

05:33.600 --> 05:35.190
This is a warehouse.

05:35.390 --> 05:36.600
It holds some goods.

05:36.750 --> 05:38.750
I want you to help me do an inventory.

05:40.270 --> 05:42.600
I have a feeling
you’re trying to trick me.

05:42.600 --> 05:44.060
How could I ever trick you?

05:44.240 --> 05:44.770
Let's go.

05:55.120 --> 05:56.630
This isn't a warehouse.

05:56.630 --> 05:58.070
It's clearly a pharmacy.

05:58.950 --> 05:59.870
Take a look at these herbs

05:59.870 --> 06:01.070
and see if they are still usable,

06:01.070 --> 06:02.120
or

06:02.120 --> 06:04.000
if you need anything else.

06:08.240 --> 06:09.480
Jewel orchid!

06:12.240 --> 06:13.950
This is the king of herbs!

06:15.600 --> 06:16.860
And reishi mushrooms!

06:18.070 --> 06:19.870
And so much ginseng!

06:22.480 --> 06:23.610
Are these all yours?

06:24.190 --> 06:25.000
Yeah.

06:25.750 --> 06:27.480
This is top-quality medicine.

06:27.480 --> 06:28.740
You've struck it rich?

06:28.870 --> 06:29.680
I...

06:30.360 --> 06:31.680
If I gave it to you,

06:31.680 --> 06:32.680
what would you do?

06:33.830 --> 06:35.750
If you gave it to me,

06:36.240 --> 06:38.040
I could definitely treat more people.

06:38.040 --> 06:39.040
In that case,

06:39.040 --> 06:41.300
I'll give you both the herbs and the shop.

06:41.560 --> 06:42.630
Are you really giving them to me?

06:42.630 --> 06:43.230
Of course.

06:45.190 --> 06:47.560
Do you have an ulterior motive?

06:49.390 --> 06:51.830
What ulterior motive
could I have with you?

06:53.240 --> 06:54.630
You’ve been treating me

06:54.630 --> 06:55.800
all this time,

06:55.870 --> 06:57.159
so after I returned to the capital,

06:57.159 --> 06:58.800
I wanted to give you something in return.

06:58.800 --> 06:59.680
But I felt

06:59.680 --> 07:01.800
that gold and silver jewelry
are too tacky.

07:01.800 --> 07:03.070
Then I thought

07:03.270 --> 07:05.070
you'd probably like a pharmacy.

07:05.070 --> 07:06.830
How can I accept

07:07.000 --> 07:08.630
such an expensive gift?

07:09.390 --> 07:10.480
Once I give it to you,

07:10.480 --> 07:12.800
won't you be able to treat more people?

07:13.240 --> 07:14.360
Then I'll really accept it?

07:14.360 --> 07:14.960
Accept it.

07:15.360 --> 07:16.490
I'll accept it then.

07:16.560 --> 07:17.750
From now on, I'll be here

07:17.750 --> 07:18.950
treating the people.

07:19.630 --> 07:20.950
Then later,

07:21.360 --> 07:22.630
I'll write an inscription for you.

07:22.630 --> 07:23.600
Save the world

07:23.600 --> 07:24.800
and bless the people.

07:24.830 --> 07:26.040
I never thought General Xiao

07:26.040 --> 07:27.680
could be so sweet-talking.

07:38.750 --> 07:40.550
You have something on your mind.

07:42.950 --> 07:45.159
I just feel the incident
at Huangpi Village

07:45.159 --> 07:46.220
is not that simple.

07:47.390 --> 07:50.600
The symptoms this time are the same
as the great plague back then.

07:50.600 --> 07:51.830
It reminds me

07:52.159 --> 07:53.360
that our Han family

07:53.360 --> 07:55.000
might have offended someone
during that plague

07:55.000 --> 07:56.040
and

07:56.040 --> 07:57.190
got persecuted.

08:00.040 --> 08:00.680
Wait.

08:00.720 --> 08:02.240
Have you thought of something?

08:02.240 --> 08:03.600
We need to investigate

08:03.600 --> 08:04.750
among those who survived

08:04.750 --> 08:05.680
that plague.

08:05.680 --> 08:07.010
Do you have any targets?

08:08.070 --> 08:10.270
The senior officials
who survived the plague

08:10.270 --> 08:12.160
include Zhang Ruizhong, Lord Zhang,

08:12.160 --> 08:14.040
and Wang Ruhai, Lord Wang.

08:16.560 --> 08:18.040
Are you saying

08:18.600 --> 08:21.040
they are all related to
the massacre of the Han family?

08:21.040 --> 08:21.630
Yes.

08:22.070 --> 08:23.330
It's highly possible.

08:23.630 --> 08:24.240
But the details

08:24.240 --> 08:26.440
can only be known after investigation.

08:26.870 --> 08:28.480
This Wang Ruhai

08:28.480 --> 08:29.800
is idle at home.

08:30.270 --> 08:31.070
It just so happens

08:31.070 --> 08:32.549
we can try starting with him.

08:32.549 --> 08:33.030
Okay.

08:35.750 --> 08:36.909
Injustice!

08:36.909 --> 08:38.630
The Prince's family is going too far!【】

08:38.630 --> 08:39.789
Let me in!

08:39.789 --> 08:40.360
Who

08:40.360 --> 08:41.669
dares to trespass into
the Prince's mansion?

08:41.669 --> 08:44.000
You lawless thugs

08:44.080 --> 08:46.670
kidnapped my daughter in broad daylight!

08:46.670 --> 08:47.120
I...

08:47.120 --> 08:48.670
I will sue you at the government office

08:48.670 --> 08:50.630
and let you get the punishment
you deserve!

08:50.630 --> 08:51.440
Sue me?

08:52.440 --> 08:54.080
Do you think the government office
will accept

08:54.080 --> 08:55.840
the lawsuit of a commoner like you?

08:55.840 --> 08:57.030
How ridiculous.

08:57.030 --> 08:58.390
Justice will prevail!

08:58.390 --> 08:59.720
I will let everyone in the world

08:59.720 --> 09:01.240
know of your evil deeds!

09:01.550 --> 09:02.630
Give me back my daughter!

09:02.630 --> 09:04.360
Give me back my daughter!

09:04.360 --> 09:04.910
You...

09:05.630 --> 09:06.510
Fine.

09:06.960 --> 09:08.080
I'll let you sue me.

09:08.240 --> 09:10.240
Let everyone see

09:10.240 --> 09:11.770
what a crazy old man you are.

09:14.030 --> 09:17.240
Give me back my daughter!

09:20.080 --> 09:20.870
My lord.

09:29.440 --> 09:31.080
This old fool

09:31.240 --> 09:32.750
has a death wish.

09:33.480 --> 09:35.670
How dare he sue me.

09:35.670 --> 09:36.670
Yes, my lord.

09:37.080 --> 09:38.810
If no one was instigating this,

09:39.000 --> 09:39.960
who in the capital

09:39.960 --> 09:41.630
would dare to cross you?

09:43.480 --> 09:44.390
Makes sense.

09:46.270 --> 09:48.670
I've been recovering at home these days.

09:48.670 --> 09:50.400
I haven't done anything wrong.

09:50.600 --> 09:52.060
Who could I have offended?

09:52.150 --> 09:54.270
Could it be that brat Xiao Chi?

09:54.840 --> 09:55.630
After all, our young master

09:55.630 --> 09:57.360
had a feud with him before.

09:58.200 --> 09:59.550
Xiao Chi?

10:01.390 --> 10:02.750
Xiao Chi!

10:03.200 --> 10:04.240
It was because of him

10:04.240 --> 10:06.480
that His Majesty made me
stay idle at home.

10:06.480 --> 10:07.000
He...

10:07.000 --> 10:08.860
Now he wants to mess with me again.

10:09.550 --> 10:10.550
He thinks

10:11.000 --> 10:11.750
that just by doing this,

10:11.750 --> 10:13.550
he can threaten the Wang family?

10:15.670 --> 10:17.670
Xiao Chi!

10:17.670 --> 10:19.330
Take that for threatening me!

10:20.120 --> 10:20.840
My lord!

10:21.440 --> 10:23.000
I spent a fortune

10:23.030 --> 10:24.480
to borrow this
from the Ministry of Justice.

10:24.480 --> 10:25.480
I still have to return it.

10:25.480 --> 10:26.670
Xiao Chi!

10:26.670 --> 10:27.870
I am not done with him.

10:53.030 --> 10:55.000
Why would I have such a nightmare?

11:38.670 --> 11:39.670
What's wrong?

11:41.480 --> 11:42.840
I had a nightmare.

11:43.270 --> 11:44.000
A nightmare?

11:45.360 --> 11:46.760
What did you dream about?

11:48.150 --> 11:51.030
I dreamed that Huangbei Village
was engulfed in flames.

11:51.030 --> 11:53.090
The villagers were all slaughtered.

11:58.360 --> 11:59.150
Come with me.

12:55.840 --> 12:56.670
Run!

12:57.360 --> 12:58.630
Hurry!

13:02.150 --> 13:03.410
How could this happen?

13:04.030 --> 13:06.490
What did these villagers
do to deserve this?

13:07.630 --> 13:09.480
We must make them pay.

13:47.480 --> 13:48.670
The hidden weapons are poisoned.

13:48.670 --> 13:49.390
Xiao Chi,

13:49.390 --> 13:50.360
hang in there.

13:50.440 --> 13:51.150
Bear with it a little longer.

13:51.150 --> 13:51.960
I'm fine.

13:52.790 --> 13:53.990
I'm glad you're okay.

13:54.080 --> 13:55.030
I'm fine.

13:55.030 --> 13:56.840
Bear with it, Xiao Chi.

14:13.390 --> 14:15.240
I'm sorry.

14:16.240 --> 14:17.080
Bear with it.

14:17.080 --> 14:18.280
Just a little longer.

14:22.870 --> 14:24.150
Hang in there.

14:25.150 --> 14:27.280
I'll go prepare some medicine for you.

14:40.600 --> 14:41.480
Boss.

14:43.750 --> 14:44.680
We don't have it.

15:08.390 --> 15:08.910
No.

15:10.240 --> 15:11.480
No.

15:33.030 --> 15:34.240
Lord Fei.

15:35.360 --> 15:36.290
Physician Wang,

15:37.630 --> 15:38.750
what kind of poison is on the dart?

15:38.750 --> 15:39.810
Have you found out?

15:39.870 --> 15:42.440
The dart is coated with
the venom of a krait.

15:43.120 --> 15:44.200
Krait venom?

15:45.550 --> 15:46.600
Is there a cure?

15:46.790 --> 15:47.910
Blue snake tail

15:47.910 --> 15:49.750
and snake herb can cure it.

15:50.000 --> 15:51.750
But these are just legends,

15:51.960 --> 15:53.220
and cannot be trusted.

15:53.270 --> 15:54.200
Physician Wang,

15:54.550 --> 15:55.670
you have been a physician for many years,

15:55.670 --> 15:57.360
and are the best physician
in Jinglan.

15:57.360 --> 15:59.390
I believe you must have other ways.

16:00.200 --> 16:01.860
As long as Xiao Chi can wake up,

16:02.080 --> 16:03.360
no matter what herbs,

16:03.480 --> 16:06.200
I, Fei Zheng, will not hesitate
even if I go bankrupt.

16:06.200 --> 16:07.600
To detoxify this,

16:07.670 --> 16:09.080
using medicine won't work.

16:09.080 --> 16:11.240
Try using poison against poison.

16:11.360 --> 16:13.240
It might be effective.

16:13.550 --> 16:14.880
Poison against poison?

16:15.390 --> 16:17.390
Physician Wang, please elaborate.

16:18.030 --> 16:20.000
We are good at using medicine,

16:20.030 --> 16:21.480
but when it comes to poison,

16:21.480 --> 16:23.030
none of us are good at it.

16:23.270 --> 16:25.200
Fortunately, Physician Han

16:25.200 --> 16:27.390
protected General Xiao's heart meridian.

16:27.390 --> 16:29.150
Even if he doesn't wake up,

16:29.150 --> 16:31.030
his condition won't worsen.

16:31.480 --> 16:32.390
So,

16:32.960 --> 16:34.630
our hope can really only rest on

16:34.630 --> 16:35.870
Physician Han.

16:36.670 --> 16:37.530
Physician Han.

16:37.550 --> 16:40.550
The herb you need is not available
in the entire capital.

16:40.550 --> 16:41.210
The Emperor

16:41.390 --> 16:42.630
has also ordered
the Imperial Medical Academy's

16:42.630 --> 16:44.760
physicians to do their best to find it.

16:45.030 --> 16:46.430
I wonder if Physician Han

16:46.550 --> 16:48.000
has any other solutions.

16:49.270 --> 16:50.840
Before we find the medicine,

16:50.840 --> 16:52.480
I'll try using other medicines

16:52.480 --> 16:54.810
to stabilize Xiao Chi's condition first.

17:18.069 --> 17:19.069
I found out.

17:19.640 --> 17:20.569
It's Wang Ruhai.

17:21.270 --> 17:22.680
Wang Ruhai?

17:24.030 --> 17:26.030
Why did he want to kill Xiao Chi?

17:27.270 --> 17:29.680
Since the general returned to the capital,

17:30.030 --> 17:31.550
he impeached Wang Ruhai,

17:32.070 --> 17:33.480
causing him to be dismissed

17:33.480 --> 17:35.160
and ostracized by his colleagues,

17:35.160 --> 17:35.880
so

17:36.160 --> 17:37.820
he wanted to kill the general.

17:38.830 --> 17:39.680
Lord Zhang

17:40.000 --> 17:41.590
is also targeting the general.

17:41.590 --> 17:43.440
Are they targeting Xiao Chi,

17:43.960 --> 17:45.480
or our Han family?

17:49.960 --> 17:51.440
This is the evidence

17:51.880 --> 17:52.400
that Xiao Chi gathered

17:52.400 --> 17:54.930
of Wang Ruhai's crimes
before he was injured.

17:55.830 --> 17:56.750
So much?

17:57.960 --> 18:00.750
Are these all the evil deeds
done by Wang Ruhai alone?

18:00.750 --> 18:02.080
This is only a part of it.

18:02.400 --> 18:03.750
There are even more

18:03.750 --> 18:06.160
petitions accusing
him and his son of bullying,

18:06.160 --> 18:07.240
running amok,

18:07.240 --> 18:08.640
and coercing trades

18:08.960 --> 18:10.560
stored in the boxes outside.

18:11.030 --> 18:12.440
I really can't figure out

18:13.000 --> 18:14.400
why the late Emperor kept

18:14.480 --> 18:16.480
someone like Wang Ruhai by his side.

18:16.590 --> 18:17.960
The late emperor suddenly

18:17.960 --> 18:19.480
fell seriously ill and passed away.

18:19.480 --> 18:20.880
There must be many things

18:21.030 --> 18:22.200
that were not thoroughly considered.

18:22.200 --> 18:22.960
However,

18:23.200 --> 18:25.800
although Wang Ruhai
has done all kinds of evil,

18:25.960 --> 18:27.960
he indeed has prestige in the court.

18:28.240 --> 18:29.240
For a man like him,

18:29.640 --> 18:31.880
who is greedy and entirely selfish,

18:32.640 --> 18:34.500
if anyone touches his interests,

18:34.880 --> 18:35.940
he will inevitably

18:36.310 --> 18:38.040
fight to the death to stop them.

18:38.640 --> 18:39.400
Then tell me,

18:39.720 --> 18:40.750
what should I do?

18:42.960 --> 18:43.620
Evil people

18:44.240 --> 18:45.370
should be punished.

18:45.480 --> 18:47.440
Since he dares to
secretly harm the Third Brother now,

18:47.440 --> 18:48.240
who knows

18:48.240 --> 18:50.970
what outrageous things
he might do in the future.

18:53.110 --> 18:53.960
The court

18:53.960 --> 18:56.400
will decide my fate.

18:56.480 --> 18:59.030
It is not your place to question me.

19:02.790 --> 19:03.960
Go back.

19:08.400 --> 19:09.590
Can you tell me

19:09.590 --> 19:12.520
the truth about
the extermination of the Han family?

19:15.270 --> 19:17.960
As for the truth
about the extermination of the Han family,

19:17.960 --> 19:19.350
even if I knew,

19:20.070 --> 19:22.110
I wouldn't tell you.

19:22.680 --> 19:23.200
You!

19:24.830 --> 19:26.000
By imperial order:

19:26.880 --> 19:27.640
all unrelated personnel

19:27.640 --> 19:28.570
are to withdraw.

19:31.440 --> 19:33.680
Investigation reveals
Wang Kun, son of Wang Ruhai,

19:33.680 --> 19:35.280
kidnapped a commoner woman.

19:35.550 --> 19:37.680
Wang Ruhai failed to discipline his son.

19:37.680 --> 19:39.160
His past crimes

19:39.240 --> 19:40.640
are too numerous to count.

19:40.640 --> 19:41.640
It is hereby ordered

19:41.640 --> 19:42.830
that he be dismissed and investigated,

19:42.830 --> 19:45.560
and his son Wang Kun
be imprisoned pending trial.

19:45.960 --> 19:47.090
This is impossible.

19:47.240 --> 19:48.370
This is impossible.

19:49.270 --> 19:49.960
Father,

19:49.960 --> 19:50.880
I'm innocent!

19:50.880 --> 19:51.480
Father,

19:51.480 --> 19:52.480
they framed me!

19:52.480 --> 19:52.960
Father!

19:52.960 --> 19:53.400
I know.

19:53.400 --> 19:53.860
Father.

19:54.240 --> 19:54.830
Save me, Father!

19:54.830 --> 19:55.240
Take him down.

19:55.240 --> 19:55.720
Don't panic.

19:55.720 --> 19:56.650
Father, save me!

19:57.310 --> 19:58.070
Father!

19:58.400 --> 19:58.880
Father!

19:59.160 --> 20:00.030
Save me, Father!

20:00.030 --> 20:00.880
Impossible. They framed me!

20:00.880 --> 20:01.830
Stop!

20:01.830 --> 20:02.680
Let go!

20:03.440 --> 20:05.700
Who dares to cause trouble in my mansion?

20:06.200 --> 20:08.030
We cannot disobey the imperial order.

20:08.030 --> 20:08.880
Take him away.

20:09.000 --> 20:09.440
Son!

20:09.440 --> 20:10.030
Father!

20:10.400 --> 20:10.920
Son!

20:11.550 --> 20:12.270
Father!

20:13.750 --> 20:14.400
Son!

20:14.400 --> 20:15.350
Save me, Father!

20:18.030 --> 20:18.720
I know.

20:18.920 --> 20:20.070
I know you are investigating

20:20.070 --> 20:21.330
the Han family matter.

20:21.350 --> 20:22.110
I

20:22.440 --> 20:23.830
will tell you the truth.

20:23.830 --> 20:25.030
Let my son go,

20:25.030 --> 20:26.400
and I'll tell you the truth.

20:26.400 --> 20:27.640
What is the truth?

20:27.640 --> 20:28.500
The truth is...

20:32.350 --> 20:33.480
Tell me now!

20:33.480 --> 20:34.550
Tell me now!

20:34.550 --> 20:37.070
What is the truth
behind the massacre of the Han family?

20:37.070 --> 20:37.960
The truth is...

20:39.000 --> 20:40.350
Wang Ruhai, tell me now!

20:40.350 --> 20:42.110
What is the truth?

21:03.640 --> 21:05.750
Eldest Princess, Wang Ruhai is dead.

21:07.270 --> 21:08.270
How did he die?

21:09.030 --> 21:10.960
When the Emperor
ordered the capture of his son,

21:10.960 --> 21:12.000
he fainted,

21:12.200 --> 21:13.880
and never woke up again.

21:14.350 --> 21:17.200
His crimes were enough
to have him paraded through the streets.

21:17.200 --> 21:18.070
Dying like this

21:18.440 --> 21:19.770
is letting him off easy.

21:20.550 --> 21:22.200
The regent left by the late Emperor

21:22.200 --> 21:23.460
is just gone like that.

21:25.240 --> 21:26.770
This is just the beginning.

21:27.640 --> 21:29.400
Lord Zhang is getting old.

21:29.680 --> 21:31.590
He probably won't last for
many more years.

21:31.590 --> 21:32.510
Then,

21:32.720 --> 21:35.270
should we secretly befriend Li Shichang?

21:35.480 --> 21:38.640
A Princess having close ties
with a minister

21:39.030 --> 21:40.760
will definitely cause gossip.

21:43.880 --> 21:45.030
Not just him.

21:45.790 --> 21:47.650
Xiao Chi has been sick for so long,

21:47.960 --> 21:50.090
and we didn't visit him either, did we?

21:51.070 --> 21:53.030
As long as the Emperor is obedient,

21:53.480 --> 21:54.640
all of Jinglan

21:55.160 --> 21:57.030
will be under my control.

21:59.550 --> 22:00.350
By the way,

22:01.550 --> 22:02.960
how is that female official?

22:02.960 --> 22:03.960
We've already arranged for her

22:03.960 --> 22:05.690
to stay in our outer residence.

22:05.750 --> 22:08.270
Everyone there belongs to
our Xie Shadow Guard.【】

22:08.270 --> 22:10.030
The tribute ambassador
from Changmo is coming soon.

22:10.030 --> 22:11.490
Keep a close eye on things.

22:11.640 --> 22:12.310
Understood.

22:12.310 --> 22:13.570
I'll take my leave now.

22:36.240 --> 22:38.300
Even though you haven't woken up yet,

22:38.590 --> 22:40.070
I believe you can

22:40.070 --> 22:41.550
hear what I'm saying.

22:43.200 --> 22:45.640
I'm going to the North Mountain
to pick an herb.

22:45.640 --> 22:46.680
With it,

22:47.000 --> 22:48.960
you will definitely wake up.

22:54.200 --> 22:56.030
You must hold on.

22:57.720 --> 22:58.920
Wait for me to return.

23:04.550 --> 23:07.000
This journey has been full of hardships,

23:07.480 --> 23:10.080
and you have always been
the one protecting me.

23:10.640 --> 23:11.790
Now it's my turn

23:12.790 --> 23:14.200
to protect you.

23:22.000 --> 23:22.830
Xiao Chi,

23:23.640 --> 23:24.440
wait for me.

23:37.960 --> 23:38.640
Lord Fei.

23:38.830 --> 23:39.550
Chengfeng,

23:42.830 --> 23:44.550
you've been guarding for quite a while.

23:44.550 --> 23:45.680
Go back and rest.

23:45.680 --> 23:46.940
I can take it from here.

23:47.680 --> 23:49.240
I wouldn't be able to sleep anyway.

23:49.240 --> 23:50.200
Being here

23:50.350 --> 23:52.270
actually makes me feel more at ease.

23:52.270 --> 23:53.070
Alright.

23:54.030 --> 23:54.640
Take a seat.

23:54.640 --> 23:56.300
I'll stay with you for a while.

23:56.350 --> 23:56.830
Sit.

26:53.880 --> 26:54.740
Physician Han.

26:56.270 --> 26:56.960
Physician Han,

26:56.960 --> 26:57.750
you're back.

27:02.160 --> 27:03.020
Physician Han!

27:03.830 --> 27:04.640
Physician Han!
